transArray.content: The hotel service is very good and very clean.

Dear guests: Hello! Thank you for your visit, and we also sincerely thank you for your love and recognition of us. We are very touched that you remember the good time here. It is our unshirkable responsibility to provide guests with a wonderful stay experience. We can get your praise. We are deeply honored. At the same time, we are more motivated to move forward and hope to have more opportunities to serve you! Manager: Ji Hongjiao
